\documentclass[12pt,a4paper]{article}
\usepackage[utf8]{inputenc}
\usepackage{graphicx}
\usepackage{xcolor}

\begin{document}

\title{Micro Soldering Journal - Lesson 1}
\author{Student}
\maketitle

\section{Embedded Controller U300}

The Embedded Controller (U300) is the SMSC MEC1324 chip.

Package: TQFP-128 (128 pins)

\begin{figure}[h]
\centering
\fbox{\parbox{0.8\textwidth}{\centering U300 Schematic Image Would Go Here \\ (Figure will be added in next iteration)}}
\caption{U300 Embedded Controller on Page 46}
\end{figure}

\subsection{Key Pins}
\begin{itemize}
    \item Pin 46: KBC\_PWR\_ON - Enables P3V3A rail
    \item Pin 57: SLP\_S3\# - Sleep state indicator
\end{itemize}

\end{document}
EOF

