\section{What is an Embedded Controller?}

The Embedded Controller (EC) is the ``brain'' of laptop power management. It controls:
\begin{itemize}
    \item Power sequencing
    \item Battery charging
    \item Keyboard scanning
    \item Thermal management
\end{itemize}

